154
00:13:31,895 --> 00:13:33,515
Thank you, my dad Yingyot,

155
00:13:33,535 --> 00:13:35,625
Aunt Nipa,

156
00:13:37,775 --> 00:13:41,225
and every single folk at the Phadetseuk Boxing Club.

157
00:13:45,275 --> 00:13:46,965
