161
00:13:59,165 --> 00:14:01,695
who has been a key driving force

162
00:14:01,715 --> 00:14:04,745
in making this big dog, Yoryak,

163
00:14:04,765 --> 00:14:07,635
believe in and love himself once again.

164
00:14:07,655 --> 00:14:09,435
Honestly,

165
00:14:09,455 --> 00:14:13,055
