187
00:16:19,525 --> 00:16:21,205
Really.

188
00:16:24,705 --> 00:16:26,045
Blue.

189
00:16:26,065 --> 00:16:26,965
Yes?

190
00:16:26,985 --> 00:16:30,535
I truly appreciate that you understand me.

191
00:16:30,555 --> 00:16:33,885
You even took your day off to run my errand with me in Chonburi.

192
00:16:35,355 --> 00:16:37,055
No need to thank me.

193
00:16:37,075 --> 00:16:39,945
I’m really fortunate to have met you.

194
00:16:39,965 --> 00:16:42,535
