236
00:19:00,965 --> 00:19:03,355
only a sticker on chat.

237
00:19:03,535 --> 00:19:07,445
Take this as a happy belated birthday.

238
00:19:08,745 --> 00:19:10,625
Thank you, Doc,

239
00:19:10,645 --> 00:19:13,245
for not forgetting my birthday.

240
00:19:13,355 --> 00:19:15,725
I told you, right?

241
00:19:15,745 --> 00:19:18,115
I never forget.

242
00:19:18,315 --> 00:19:21,245
Those who are important in my life,

243
00:19:21,265 --> 00:19:23,395
